relation: Eia Ka Halawai Ana Kuahiwi Hawai'i..... Here is the gathering of the mountains of Hawai'i
He Puna Wai Ola O Na Pua..... It's the wellsprings for the blossoms (progeny)
Eia Na Wai Puna Hawai'i..... Here are the waters of Hawai'i
E Ola Na Pua I Ka Malu 'Ai..... Life in peace and comfort
Eia Na Pua Hawai'i..... Here are the progeny of Hawai'i
E Ola Kahua Kukulu Kanawai A Loina..... Life to the foundation of law and protocol
Eia Kekaulike..... Here is balance and equality
O Ka Hale O Ku, O Ke Hale O Noho..... Where the house stands, there man dwells
Eia No Ka Ho'i..... Here it is / It is correct.
